  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="904226398">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-904226398" class="vote-count">2</span>
              <a id="btn-904226398" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="904226398">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Nokia5610/">Dr. ChaLove</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/904226398">2015-03-18 16:32:09</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">片段式的文字就特别适合片段式的阅读。每隔一段时间读一段，感觉就进去了两位主角的内心，体验到他们的期盼和纠结。我在高中的周记本也写过这样的“小说”，初衷是磨练文笔和分享“干货”。用一种充满激情和天真的态度去谈情说爱、高谈阔论。这种两地书，满足了我的思想偷窥癖。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1030470/?comment_id=904226398"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
